name: Custom Sales Partners Commission
query:
SELECT
    name as "Sales Invoice:Link/Sales Invoice:130",
    posting_date as "Date::80",
    customer "Customer:Link/Customer:150",
    po_no as "PO#:Data:80",
    sales_rep_sm as "SM#:Data:100",
    sales_partner as "Sales Partner:Link/Sales Partner:140",
	sum(net_total) as "Amount:Currency:90",
	sum(total_commission) as "Commission:Currency:60",
	sum(total_commission)*100/sum(net_total) as "Rate:Float:50",
        payments_made as "Pmts:Currency:90",
        payment_details as "Pmt JV:Link/Journal Voucher:80",
        (sum(total_commission) - payments_made) as "Comm Due:Currency:60" 
FROM
	`tabSales Invoice`
WHERE
	docstatus = 1 and ifnull(net_total, 0) > 0 and ifnull(total_commission, 0) > 0 and outstanding_amount = 0.00
GROUP BY
	name
ORDER BY
	"Total Commission:Currency:120"
